1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 3=

3
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:19,160
Weren't we going to ambush her?

4
00:00:19,359 --> 00:00:21,120
Why the sudden change to poisoning?

5
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:23,039
We might not take her even in an ambush.

6
00:00:23,039 --> 00:00:24,440
Poison is a safer bet.

7
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,760
What if I'm immune to all toxins?

8
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:29,160
(Qian, Li Wan's henchman)
Then, we'll have to do it the hard way.

9
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:33,890
Don't be afraid of her.

10
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,580
Just get it done!

11
00:00:36,719 --> 00:00:37,880
Mark my words, Chu Yunchang,

12
00:00:38,159 --> 00:00:39,975
this isn't over between us!

13
00:00:40,119 --> 00:00:42,039
(Oh no, why is she back?)

14
00:00:42,399 --> 00:00:43,000
(Whatever.)

15
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,350
(I'll just pretend I can't fight.)

16
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:48,119
Qian!

17
00:00:48,119 --> 00:00:49,119
A one-hit knockout!

18
00:00:49,719 --> 00:00:51,359
You really were hiding your strength.

19
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,240
Wait, did I really just do that?

20
00:00:53,719 --> 00:00:54,520
You certainly did!

21
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:56,799
Who are you people?

22
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,039
What about her?

23
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,880
Forget it, just tie them both up!

24
00:01:05,925 --> 00:01:06,565
Yunchang?

25
00:01:10,790 --> 00:01:11,599
(Where did she go?)

26
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,400
Oh no, this is bad.

27
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:18,319
Buyu!

28
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,239
A girl named Zhizhi just came by.

29
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,120
The Three-Hand Sect

30
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,239
kidnapped Rong and Chang.

31
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:23,519
I also just got a tip.

32
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,930
Unusual activity
in the western outskirts.

33
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:25,560
Let's go.

34
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:26,480
I'll gather the men.

35
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,159
No time for that!

36
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,200
Why would those thieves kidnap you?

37
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,079
How should I know?

38
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,640
I'm a victim here, too.

39
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:38,280
Maybe they're trying to

40
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:40,359
extort money from my aunt and uncle.

41
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,799
Even now, you won't tell the truth?

42
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:44,239
That man called Li Wan

43
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,879
is the leader of the Three-Hand Sect.

44
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,799
What even is the Three-Hand Sect?

45
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:51,120
He came to your birthday!

46
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,879
Stop pretending.

47
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:54,879
That was only out of respect
for my aunt and uncle.

48
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:55,920
Chu Yunchang,

49
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,280
my brother

50
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,000
takes his feelings very seriously.

51
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:01,159
I really hope you aren't
just playing with him.

52
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,040
I take my feelings seriously, too.

53
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,080
As long as he stays true to me,

54
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,439
I would give my life for him.

55
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,439
And here I thought you were capable.

56
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:19,159
Turns out you're nothing special.

57
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,639
If I'd known,
I wouldn't have bothered Qian.

58
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:23,840
I could've saved
a thousand taels of silver.

59
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,560
He said your martial arts were weak.

60
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:26,919
You outnumbered us.

61
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:27,900
There's no honor in this.

62
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:28,479
Ha!

63
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:30,199
You're in no place to gloat.

64
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:31,680
Now that you're toast,

65
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:33,479
any last words?

66
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:36,759
What if my aunt and uncle find you?

67
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:41,080
You really think I'm afraid
of the King of Thieves?

68
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:44,159
The King of Thieves?

69
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:45,719
How is your uncle part of this?

70
00:02:45,719 --> 00:02:46,919
Didn't I tell you to shut up?

71
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:47,840
Shut your mouth!

72
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,000
You shut your mouth!

73
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,210
Do you have any idea who I am?

74
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:51,639
She's right.

75
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,639
This has nothing to do with her.

76
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,879
Let her go.

77
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,639
Otherwise, you'll face
dire consequences.

78
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,479
Chu Yunchang,

79
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,199
don't get too cocky.

80
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:00,439
Right now,

81
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,159
you aren't the one in charge.

82
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:04,270
I am Mao Wenrong
of the Gate Bureau's Intel Corps.

83
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,879
If you're smart, you'll release me now.

84
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,479
You're from the Gate Bureau?

85
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:11,120
Perfect. Now I have evidence
of your collusion with them.

86
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:13,360
She's bluffing.

87
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:13,960
Nonsense.

88
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:15,430
Here's my badge!

89
00:03:16,610 --> 00:03:17,879
You really are with the Bureau.

90
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,120
Then, I definitely can't let you leave.

91
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:22,840
You two are quite the beauties, too.

92
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:26,719
Don't blame me for what happens next.

93
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:27,919
Don't you dare!

94
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,039
Rong...

95
00:03:31,330 --> 00:03:32,319
Don't get the wrong idea.

96
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,159
I still don't like you.

97
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,759
But as a constable,

98
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:36,800
I refuse to allow any crime

99
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,990
to be committed in my presence.

100
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,560
If you touch us,

101
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,159
the Gate Bureau will hunt you down.

102
00:03:42,159 --> 00:03:44,240
Quite feisty, aren't you?

103
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:47,879
I know you want to save Rong,

104
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:48,960
but we could be outnumbered.

105
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,960
That doesn't matter now!

106
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,580
My sister and Chang were taken
quite a while ago.

107
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:53,620
We can't delay any longer!

108
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,639
Who's there?

109
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,439
Surround them!

110
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,390
This is Three-Hand Sect's territory!

111
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,199
Die!

112
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,280
Buyu, stay close to me.

113
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,000
I'll protect you!

114
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,759
Let one escape.

115
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,759
Don't you dare!

116
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:22,560
With such a beautiful little lady,

117
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,519
why wouldn't I dare?

118
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:24,260
Run while you can!

119
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,199
I'll kill you!

120
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:33,600
Sect Leader Li,

121
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,839
did you forget about me already?

122
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:40,759
Li Wan,

123
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,720
you betrayed the Martial Alliance,

124
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,040
then you defected to Lin Xin'er.

125
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:46,279
And now, you're preying
on innocent women.

126
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,240
Your crimes are heinous.

127
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:50,290
As the Grandmaster
of the Martial Alliance,

128
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:52,160
I shall purge the ranks!

129
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,279
You didn't need our help.

130
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,959
What happened to her?

131
00:05:03,399 --> 00:05:04,959
She was knocked unconscious

132
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:05,959
trying to save me.

133
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,279
It seems he wanted to use you as a gift

134
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,800
to join the Southern Thieves.

135
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:12,199
Chang,

136
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:14,519
Mao Wenrong is a government official.

137
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,560
If she wakes up and talks,

138
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,780
how will you explain yourself?

139
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:19,240
She didn't see a thing.

140
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:23,040
Mao Wenrong might be difficult,

141
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,279
but she tried to protect me.

142
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,279
We can't hurt her.

143
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,959
We shouldn't stay here.

144
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:29,879
Let's head back.

145
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,720
I'll help carry her.

146
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:33,959
The Three-Hand Sect wouldn't
gather for no reason.

147
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:36,079
They might stir up more trouble.

148
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:36,990
I need to check it out.

149
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:38,519
No need.

150
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,920
When we came,

151
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,319
we already notified the Gate Bureau.

152
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,920
So Buyu is coming too?

153
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,879
Rong and I can't leave yet.

154
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,879
So Buyu really is with the Gate Bureau.

155
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,040
Why did you lie to me?

156
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:50,319
Now is not the time to settle that.

157
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:51,519
Let's head out first.

158
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,959
I didn't tell you
about Buyu's background

159
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:59,839
because I didn't want you to worry.

160
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:01,839
You guys go ahead.

161
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,480
He won't catch me.

162
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:06,480
What about you and her
being kidnapped for no reason?

163
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,959
Have you thought of
an explanation for Mao Buyu?

164
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:10,610
I'll say it's
because of your bad friends.

165
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,079
They saw how wealthy we are,

166
00:06:12,079 --> 00:06:12,920
so they snatched me.

167
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,519
You little brat.

168
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:39,560
Jade Squirrel.

169
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,920
It really is you.

170
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:42,600
As Grandmaster of the martial world,

171
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,360
you instigated the Three-Hand Sect
to abduct my sister and fiancée.

172
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:46,639
What exactly are you after?

173
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:47,959
They aren't...

174
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:59,439
This won't stop me from arresting you.

175
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,319
The Jade Squirrel!

176
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,279
Gao Shun!

177
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,480
Stop the chase.

178
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:11,680
Saving my sister and Chang comes first.

179
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,519
She's injured. She won't get far.

180
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,120
Yunchang!

181
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:29,279
Yunchang! Chu Yunchang!

182
00:07:29,279 --> 00:07:31,480
Help! Someone, help!

183
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,160
Quickly, help!

184
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,759
Help!

185
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,639
Chang!

186
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:36,199
Buyu!

187
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:37,439
Chang!

188
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,160
Who did this?

189
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,800
It had to be Li Wan.

190
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:43,199
He tried to assault me.

191
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:44,120
Yunchang, she...

192
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:45,360
It's my fault.

193
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,759
Yunchang was injured while saving me.

194
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,839
She's badly hurt.

195
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,360
We must get her a doctor now.

196
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:59,187
(Rising Clouds)

197
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:06,079
Buyu,

198
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,439
it's all my fault.

199
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,759
As a constable,

200
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:10,439
I failed to protect Chu Yunchang.

201
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:12,199
Instead, she took such a heavy blow

202
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,480
just to save my life.

203
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:15,079
We have to do everything we can

204
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:16,279
to help her recover.

205
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:18,639
The best healer in the city

206
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:20,040
is already treating Chang.

207
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,120
She'll be fine.

208
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,639
Chang!

209
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:27,920
Mrs. Mei, Squire Mei.

210
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:29,319
How is she?

211
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:31,079
The doctor is still with her.

212
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,159
This is on you!

213
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,159
You did this to her!

214
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,720
Don't blame Buyu. It was me.

215
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,399
Yunchang was saving me...

216
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,200
Our Chang grew up
without a scratch on her.

217
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,480
But since the day she met you two,

218
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,159
it's been nothing but trouble.

219
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,080
Get out!

220
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,759
You aren't welcome here!

221
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:55,799
We are at fault.

222
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,519
But I'm not leaving

223
00:08:58,679 --> 00:09:00,799
until she wakes up
and I know she's alright.

224
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:03,639
Buyu,

225
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:05,799
maybe we should head back for now.

226
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,279
We can return once they've calmed down.

227
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:10,559
I remember we have
some premium herbs at home.

228
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:12,679
Let's go fetch some for Ms. Chu.

229
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:14,320
We don't want your herbs!

230
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:20,200
Let them all in.

231
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:21,559
You're badly hurt.

232
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:23,000
It's best if you don't speak.

233
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:24,279
Come in.

234
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:33,679
Chang...

235
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:35,879
I'm fine.

236
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:39,120
Ms. Chu's abdominal injury is severe.

237
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,320
She's lost a lot of blood.

238
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:41,559
For the next few days,

239
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:43,120
you must watch her diet carefully

240
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,519
and ensure she gets plenty of rest.

241
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:46,559
She must not overexert herself.

242
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:49,000
The wound was quite deep.

243
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:51,000
Though I've managed to stitch it,

244
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,639
it will likely leave a scar.

245
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,360
Thank you, sir.

246
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:59,480
Zhizhi, go with the doctor
to get the herbs.

247
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,039
Follow me.

248
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,480
Are you still in pain?

249
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:16,440
I'm fine.

250
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,320
Don't worry.

251
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:19,320
Chang,

252
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:20,919
you've suffered a heavy injury.

253
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,440
You should save your strength.

254
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:28,080
Chang, your injuries are severe.

255
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,559
It's best that you rest now.

256
00:10:30,519 --> 00:10:32,480
I'll fetch some precious herbs for you.

257
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:44,559
Yunchang,

258
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,279
I was wrong before.

259
00:10:46,559 --> 00:10:47,759
I shouldn't have doubted you.

260
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,120
Focus on your recovery.

261
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,639
We'll come back to visit you soon.

262
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:55,159
Let's go.

263
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:01,399
Chang,

264
00:11:01,879 --> 00:11:03,399
don't be a hero just because

265
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,399
you're a good fighter.

266
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:06,399
You nearly lost your life

267
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:08,000
because of Mao Buyu.

268
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:12,200
At least the outcome was good.

269
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,639
Rong accepts me now.

270
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,879
Well, I don't approve!

271
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,000
Their entire family is
with the Gate Bureau.

272
00:11:21,310 --> 00:11:23,399
Besides, Mao Buyu is the reason
you're in this state.

273
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,960
I will never agree to this marriage.

274
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:29,240
Chang,

275
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:30,559
get some rest.

276
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,279
Your aunt is just upset.

277
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:32,840
Right?

278
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,000
What are you doing?

279
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,720
Let's go.

280
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:39,639
Let's go.

281
00:11:47,112 --> 00:11:50,387
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

282
00:11:50,425 --> 00:11:53,300
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

283
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:59,518
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

284
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:04,020
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

285
00:12:04,150 --> 00:12:07,070
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

286
00:12:08,238 --> 00:12:13,478
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

287
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:17,093
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

288
00:12:17,093 --> 00:12:20,743
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

289
00:12:20,812 --> 00:12:24,302
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

290
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:27,375
♪To the ends of time♪

291
00:12:27,375 --> 00:12:30,750
♪The moon traces your face♪

292
00:12:30,937 --> 00:12:34,525
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

293
00:12:34,525 --> 00:12:40,765
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

294
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:44,315
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

295
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:48,138
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

296
00:12:48,425 --> 00:12:51,450
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

297
00:12:51,450 --> 00:12:54,550
♪On our way to forever♪

298
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:58,400
♪The moon traces your face♪

299
00:12:58,400 --> 00:13:01,760
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

300
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:07,910
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

301
00:13:08,987 --> 00:13:18,627
♪Just to be with you♪

